        A convenience method that determines if this NodeSet contains a specific entity.
        Parameters:
        e - The entity to test for
        Returns:

      • isSingleton

        boolean isSingleton()
        Determines if this NodeSet is a singleton. A NodeSet is a singleton if it contains only one Node.
        Returns:
